Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:07.67,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1386460,1387670}Ayuhara-san?{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:11.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388670,1391510}I understood a little about your charm.{NOTE:御守の訳が少し分かったわ。}
